I'm surprised you would say that.

9
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:08,640
Actually, I'm fond of peach blossoms,

10
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:11,000
[so I picked one with that embroidery.]

11
00:02:11,920 --> 00:02:12,960
Oh, I see.

12
00:02:13,480 --> 00:02:15,000
No wonder it looks so familiar.

13
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:17,400
So this embroidery pattern

14
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:18,560
is the one I've seen

15
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:19,600
in a pre-made boutique.

16
00:02:19,920 --> 00:02:20,880
[This is indeed]

17
00:02:20,880 --> 00:02:22,039
[a trendy style this year.]

18
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,879
If I recall correctly,

19
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:27,280
it has an outer garment.

20
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,720
Why aren't you wearing it?

21
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:40,240
I might have forgotten it in the rush.

22
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:43,680
I can't remember where I left it.

23
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:46,560
You seem to be quite busy tonight.

24
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:49,000
In chaos, errors are inevitable.

25
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,240
Then what is this powder?

26
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,040
What could it be?

27
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,800
[If I'm not mistaken,]

28
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:08,960
this should be the fabled

29
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:10,080
mandrake fragrance.

30
00:03:11,920 --> 00:03:12,720
[I...]

31
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,400
I've never heard

32
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,800
of that.

33
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,360
I also don't know

34
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,600
how it ended up on me.

35
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:19,520
[Please see the truth!]

36
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:20,720
[The abduction of Lady Du]

37
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:21,840
truly has nothing to do with me!

38
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,080
Really?

39
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:24,960
Jing Lin!

40
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,360
[Xu Jize,]

41
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:30,240
[this piece of garment]

42
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,640
was discovered by us on the way,

43
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,520
is it yours?

44
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,160
Are you trying

45
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,760
to deny it?

46
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:52,000
In your escape, you panicked

47
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:54,440
and discarded your outer garment,

48
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,440
not realizing that

49
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:57,440
the silver thread on the collar

50
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:59,080
got caught on the inner.

51
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,640
You also forgot

52
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:02,360
that the inner pocket

53
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:04,640
still held the mandrake powder.

54
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,280
[And this powder]

55
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:08,480
[has also remained on the inner garment.]

56
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:13,520
[Xu Jize,]

57
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,640
you used the powder to sedate the bride.

58
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:16,560
You're a repeat offender,

59
00:04:16,840 --> 00:04:18,600
and the mastermind behind this.

60
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:20,520
You even killed your accomplice!

61
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,600
No!

62
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,080
That's not true!

63
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,720
I didn't kill anyone!

64
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:26,040
I didn't!

65
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:27,320
Sir,

66
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:29,120
I did use the powder,

67
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:30,680
'cause I was captivated by the bride.

68
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:32,000
[But...]

69
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,240
I really didn't kill anyone!

70
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,880
Such a shameless person,

71
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,360
