85
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,960
[I used to believe that]

86
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:26,600
jade-like

87
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:29,360
beauties are waiting for you in books.

88
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:32,200
[But after becoming a wedding attendant,]

89
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,840
I've come to realize

90
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:38,600
that those aren't crucial.

91
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:43,960
With just a whiff of mandrake fragrance,

92
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:47,560
even the most secluded bride

93
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:50,680
can become my own object of delight.

94
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:53,240
[Because these subtle words]

95
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:54,760
[cannot be spoken,]

96
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:57,320
I often succeed

97
00:05:58,240 --> 00:06:00,000
and no one is able to speak out.

98
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:03,000
Then why did you set your sights

99
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:04,680
on Lady Du this time?

100
00:06:05,080 --> 00:06:06,600
I have no particular hobbies,

101
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:09,440
just a fondness for fair ladies.

102
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,240
I have long heard of

103
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:12,640
[her beauty.]

104
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:15,200
How could I possibly miss such an

105
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:17,280
opportunity to be with

106
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:19,200
the renowned beauty of Yingzhou?

107
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,560
What's the name

108
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,160
of your accomplice,

109
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:25,120
the deceased, I mean,

110
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:26,800
[and your connection to him?]

111
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:29,760
He was just a petty criminal.

112
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,440
All I know is that he goes by

113
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,200
the name scummy.

114
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:35,440
[He's an orphan]

115
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:37,920
[and has served time in prison.]

116
00:06:38,280 --> 00:06:40,000
Long before the man in black showed up,

117
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,840
you're already in a heated argument.

118
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:42,880
What's that for?

119
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:52,320
I decided to end the abduction,

120
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:54,240
and bring Lady Du back.

121
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:54,960
Hey,

122
00:06:55,080 --> 00:06:56,040
I made a mistake.

123
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:57,000
Let her go.

124
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:58,360
Be serious!

125
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,680
The die is cast.

126
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,800
You have to go through with it!

127
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:02,520
It's a mistake! We should let her go!

128
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:02,920
You...

129
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:07,000
[Suddenly, a noise came from a distance.]

130
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:08,280
I'll check over there.

131
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:12,120
[I suspected someone was tailing us,]

132
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:14,040
[so I the argument ended.]

133
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:15,920
[He's]

134
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:17,320
[tasked with keeping Lady Du]

135
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:18,560
[in the well.]

136
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,600
[I went to check the surrounding area.]

137
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:22,240
[But I found nothing.]

138
00:07:23,080 --> 00:07:24,400
[Maybe it's just a stray cat, I assume.]

139
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:25,160
Bro,

140
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:26,480
I didn't see anything,

141
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:28,040
just a feral cat in the bushes.

142
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:29,760
Perhaps it made the sound.

143
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,400
[I was in complete shock,]

144
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,360
[fearing that the murderer would return]

145
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:36,720
[and kill me as well,]

146
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,560
[so I ran away.]

147
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,280
Xu Jize,

148
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:42,040
about the murderer

149
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,080
you mentioned,

150
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:44,680
[is there any other witness who saw him?]

151
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:48,000
Then,

152
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:49,240
how can you prove

153
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,960
that you didn't argue and that

154
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:52,680
he wasn't killed by you?

155
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:57,680
If I had to fight with him,

156
00:07:58,160 --> 00:08:00,320
he'd definitely have had the upper hand.

157
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:02,240
[What strength do I possess]

158
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,680
[to manage to kill him?]

159
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:04,920
Sir,

160
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,360
please see the truth...

161
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:09,240
For his death,

162
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,640
[I'll conduct a thorough investigation]

163
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:11,920
before a decision.

164
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:14,320
The evidence in Lady Du's case is solid.

165
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:15,800
[Someone!]

166
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:18,520
[Detain the convict Xu Jize!]

167
00:08:18,520 --> 00:08:19,160
Yes, sir!

168
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,400
Move!

169
00:08:56,760 --> 00:08:57,560
Hey, aren't you

170
00:08:57,800 --> 00:08:59,800
gonna sleep after a whole night of fuss?

171
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:02,680
Is the fearless Lady Yan so

172
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,840
scared of sharing a bed with her husband?

173
00:09:06,040 --> 00:09:07,720
I do want to sleep,

174
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:08,880
but as soon as I lie down, my mind

175
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:10,360
is filled with thoughts of the case.

176
00:09:10,560 --> 00:09:12,160
It's resolved smoothly, but I

177
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:14,560
can't shake the sense of hidden truths.

178
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:15,480
Smoothly?

179
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,600
I chased the suspect until midnight,

180
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:19,600
and it took him a long time to confess.

181
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,440
And it's only after being tortured

182
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:21,760
he finally revealed everything.

183
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:23,320
What I'm referring to

184
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:25,280
is not just the bride abduction case.

185
00:09:25,560 --> 00:09:27,000
Even though it's closed,

186
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,600
with the kidnapper scummy dead,

187
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,600
there's a new murder case to deal with.

188
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,440
He's a mere thug.

189
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,520
Here in Yingzhou,

190
00:09:34,640 --> 00:09:35,840
he must have had many personal grudges.

191
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:37,800
What kind of grudges

192
00:09:37,800 --> 00:09:39,320
would lead to such a convoluted plot,

193
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:40,520
killing him and

194
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:42,280
then removing his eyes?

195
00:09:42,760 --> 00:09:44,560
Was the appearance of the murderer

196
00:09:44,560 --> 00:09:45,920
a coincidence, or was it all premeditated?

197
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:47,560
It's difficult to figure out right now.

198
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:48,960
You should get some rest.

199
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:51,000
But I can't fall asleep.

200
00:09:51,160 --> 00:09:52,920
Among his friends and family,

201
00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:55,040
the most probable suspect would be...

202
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:02,920
Since you're so energetic,

203
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:05,960
why not do something else?

204
00:10:08,400 --> 00:10:09,200
You...

205
00:10:10,520 --> 00:10:11,720
What are you up to?

206
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,120
You know,

207
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:23,080
as your husband...

208
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:26,720
You...

209
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:31,760
Out of your mind?

210
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:34,000
They dub me the White Death,

211
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:35,800
my word is law,

212
00:10:35,800 --> 00:10:36,800
my oaths unwavering.

213
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,920
Yet in your sight, my love,

214
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:41,280
I am merely a lunatic, huh?

215
00:10:53,800 --> 00:10:55,120
What did you give me?

216
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:57,680
Slumber Pill.

217
00:10:58,240 --> 00:10:59,560
It can help you fall asleep.

218
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,680
Sweet dreams, my love.

219
00:11:04,680 --> 00:11:05,480
[My Lord.]

220
00:11:06,640 --> 00:11:07,440
[My Lord.]

221
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:08,640
A letter from Xiang'an.

222
00:11:09,520 --> 00:11:10,680
Why is it so urgent?

223
00:11:11,560 --> 00:11:12,840
The lady is just about to sleep,

224
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:14,400
and I haven't let you in yet.

225
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,080
Apologies.

226
00:11:16,520 --> 00:11:17,800
But as asked, I have to

227
00:11:17,920 --> 00:11:19,120
report such letters instantly.

228
00:11:22,680 --> 00:11:23,880
An urgent letter from Xiang'an?

229
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:25,240
Who sent it?

230
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:26,920
Lady Xu.

231
00:11:51,680 --> 00:11:53,000
There's nothing discreet about it.

232
00:11:56,040 --> 00:11:57,200
Would you read it first, my love?

233
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,040
Nope,

234
00:12:00,280 --> 00:12:02,040
I'm not interested in your love letters.

235
00:12:02,520 --> 00:12:03,800
I'm gonna sleep.

236
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:06,600
Lady Xu and I are not

237
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:08,040
romantically involved!

238
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:11,040
Besides, the one I care about

239
00:12:11,040 --> 00:12:12,240
is someone else.

240
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:16,560
Yan Xing?

241
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:54,200
It really takes effect at the right time.

242
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:21,160
[We are Masked Specters.]

243
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:24,120
[When are you going to find my head?]

244
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:27,280
[Hand over your head!]

245
00:13:27,760 --> 00:13:28,680
[Who's there?]

246
00:13:32,760 --> 00:13:33,560
[Who is it?]

247
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:35,600
[Show yourself now!]

248
00:13:35,880 --> 00:13:36,880
[My eyes...]

249
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:39,760
[My eyes!]

250
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:41,040
No!

251
00:14:02,560 --> 00:14:03,440
Is this...

252
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:06,080
a red-feathered gray pigeon?

253
00:14:08,160 --> 00:14:09,760
[The arrival of this pigeon]

254
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:11,760
[indicates that there are]

255
00:14:11,760 --> 00:14:12,400
[definitely undercover agents]

256
00:14:12,400 --> 00:14:13,440
[from Her Highness in Yingzhou]

257
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:14,400
[who cannot show themselves.]

258
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:16,960
[The pigeon is a signal]

259
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,760
[that I should report to the capital.]

260
00:14:18,760 --> 00:14:19,560
Xing!

261
00:14:20,800 --> 00:14:21,600
Hi, Xing.

262
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:26,880
Did you bring this gray pigeon?

263
00:14:29,520 --> 00:14:31,080
Are you...

264
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:31,840
No,

265
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:33,280
I just saw it hovering

266
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:34,520
in your courtyard,

267
00:14:34,520 --> 00:14:35,400
refusing to leave.

268
00:14:36,160 --> 00:14:36,960
Have you

269
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:38,560
heard of the legend?

270
00:14:38,720 --> 00:14:39,560
If a red-feathered gray pigeon

271
00:14:39,560 --> 00:14:40,440
makes its home at your place,

272
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:41,840
it means you will have great fortune.

273
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:42,920
You must keep it.

274
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:44,680
So I hurried to the street

275
00:14:44,680 --> 00:14:45,920
to buy you a birdcage.

276
00:14:46,400 --> 00:14:47,200
Is that so?

277
00:14:49,560 --> 00:14:50,360
So you came

278
00:14:50,360 --> 00:14:51,800
to bring me the cage?

279
00:14:52,640 --> 00:14:53,600
There's one more thing.

280
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:55,480
We've run out of deer antlers.

281
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:58,120
However, Gannan is low on herb reserves.

282
00:14:58,120 --> 00:14:59,360
I've checked in the largest healing house,

283
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:00,200
Guangchun Hall.

284
00:15:00,280 --> 00:15:01,040
But they said they've never stored

285
00:15:01,040 --> 00:15:02,360
such a rare item.

286
00:15:02,800 --> 00:15:04,120
They only have Cistanche.

287
00:15:04,240 --> 00:15:06,440
It may need to be sourced from elsewhere.

