00:15:56,160 --> 00:15:56,960
Even the pots for decoction

301
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:58,320
have to be custom-made this large.

302
00:15:58,400 --> 00:16:00,120
They shouldn't be for decoction,

303
00:16:00,160 --> 00:16:01,920
but rather for storing herbs.

304
00:16:04,680 --> 00:16:05,560
By the way, Yeyun, I asked you

305
00:16:05,720 --> 00:16:07,440
to keep an eye on the provincial office

306
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:08,640
for any suspicious individuals.

307
00:16:08,640 --> 00:16:09,640
Have you found anyone?

308
00:16:09,640 --> 00:16:10,840
Sis, your instructions are something

309
00:16:10,840 --> 00:16:12,480
I have definitely taken to heart.

310
00:16:13,160 --> 00:16:15,480
I haven't spotted anyone for now,

311
00:16:15,480 --> 00:16:16,400
but I did learn about

312
00:16:16,400 --> 00:16:17,640
a suspicious place.

313
00:16:18,440 --> 00:16:20,760
I've heard there's an inner chamber

314
00:16:20,760 --> 00:16:22,080
that no one is allowed to enter,

315
00:16:22,520 --> 00:16:24,480
yet Lord Mo frequently visits it himself.

316
00:16:39,440 --> 00:16:41,480
[Yingzhou is a harsh and frigid place,]

317
00:16:41,760 --> 00:16:43,520
[but it boasts such vibrant peonies.]

318
00:16:44,720 --> 00:16:45,920
[Pink peonies?]

319
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:49,000
Lord Shen, this way please.

320
00:16:49,080 --> 00:16:49,520
Very well.

321
00:17:00,560 --> 00:17:02,120
What brings him here?

322
00:17:50,520 --> 00:17:51,840
Yingzhou's situated in the northern cold region.

323
00:17:52,680 --> 00:17:53,920
It often experiences snowfall in winter.

324
00:17:55,800 --> 00:17:57,520
To have such a warm room to nurture flowers

325
00:18:01,880 --> 00:18:03,600
must have required considerable effort.

326
00:18:11,600 --> 00:18:12,400
Qianzhi.

327
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:25,320
Lord Shen.

328
00:18:40,280 --> 00:18:41,200
Do you have to distance yourself

329
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:42,280
from me?

330
00:18:46,960 --> 00:18:47,800
In this day and age,

331
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:50,240
your position is quite significant.

332
00:18:50,520 --> 00:18:51,360
I have experienced the trials

333
00:18:51,360 --> 00:18:52,800
and tribulations of officialdom.

334
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:54,320
I simply wish to live a stable life and

335
00:18:54,480 --> 00:18:56,040
have no desire to climb the social ladder

336
00:18:56,200 --> 00:18:57,520
or create difficulties for you.

337
00:18:58,400 --> 00:18:59,840
I hope you can understand.

338
00:19:02,800 --> 00:19:03,760
In public,

339
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:06,080
I understand your reluctance

340
00:19:06,760 --> 00:19:07,920
to be associated with me.

341
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:09,880
But now it's just the two of us.

342
00:19:11,720 --> 00:19:12,560
Do you truly wish to keep me

343
00:19:12,560 --> 00:19:14,000
at a distance?

344
00:19:23,880 --> 00:19:24,680
Back then,

345
00:19:25,920 --> 00:19:27,320
you were imprisoned

346
00:19:27,960 --> 00:19:29,120
and endured great suffering.

347
00:19:29,920 --> 00:19:30,920
In the end,

348
00:19:31,080 --> 00:19:32,200
it's the politics of officialdom

349
00:19:32,200 --> 00:19:33,040
that have entangled you.

350
00:19:33,520 --> 00:19:34,720
So from that moment on,

351
00:19:34,840 --> 00:19:35,800
I wished to keep

352
00:19:35,840 --> 00:19:36,520
you away from any

353
00:19:36,520 --> 00:19:37,880
further ties to officialdom.

354
00:19:38,440 --> 00:19:39,400
But I never anticipated

355
00:19:40,520 --> 00:19:41,680
that your exceptional talent

356
00:19:42,120 --> 00:19:43,240
would still draw

357
00:19:43,520 --> 00:19:45,280
the attention of Her Highness.

358
00:19:46,800 --> 00:19:47,600
Now, you hold the position

359
00:19:47,640 --> 00:19:48,880
of the commander of Imperial Guard,

360
00:19:49,760 --> 00:19:50,560
while I,

361
00:19:51,640 --> 00:19:53,200
can only remain a lower ranking official.

362
00:20:00,480 --> 00:20:01,440
I see.

363
00:20:03,920 --> 00:20:05,680
So you're blaming me, Qianzhi.

364
00:20:07,600 --> 00:20:08,920
Exceptional talent?

365
00:20:10,320 --> 00:20:12,120
Drawing attention?

366
00:20:12,920 --> 00:20:14,080
The old acquaintances of the Shen Family,

367
00:20:14,200 --> 00:20:15,320
my father's old friends,

368
00:20:15,840 --> 00:20:17,600
who doesn't know that

369
00:20:18,120 --> 00:20:20,280
I relied on selling my father for status,

370
00:20:20,280 --> 00:20:21,920
and forced my own mother to her death

371
00:20:22,480 --> 00:20:23,960
just to escape punishment.

372
00:20:24,760 --> 00:20:25,880
[I hereby report!]

373
00:20:27,360 --> 00:20:29,800
[The traitor Shen Bingzhu's son, Shen Du]

374
00:20:30,920 --> 00:20:32,280
[accuses my father]

375
00:20:38,480 --> 00:20:40,120
Such despicable behavior

376
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:46,640
is something everyone can scorn.

377
00:20:48,800 --> 00:20:50,240
Especially you, Qianzhi.

378
00:20:51,520 --> 00:20:53,240
You must feel a deep regret.

379
00:20:55,800 --> 00:20:57,320
Back then, on the path of the palace,

380
00:20:58,040 --> 00:20:59,600
you knelt all the way to the palace

381
00:21:06,040 --> 00:21:08,040
to plead for Shen Family...

382
00:21:10,760 --> 00:21:11,560
[Your Majesty!]

383
00:21:12,440 --> 00:21:13,920
[Lord Shen has been wronged!]

384
00:21:20,280 --> 00:21:21,160
[Your Majesty!]

385
00:21:22,080 --> 00:21:25,120
[The Shens' women and children are innocent!]

386
00:21:36,800 --> 00:21:38,640
The late emperor spared us,

387
00:21:39,040 --> 00:21:39,880
considering your loyalty, thus avoiding

388
00:21:39,880 --> 00:21:41,400
the death penalty for my mother and me.

389
00:21:43,720 --> 00:21:45,920
And I was able to enter the Custodial Ward.

390
00:21:45,960 --> 00:21:46,760
There's no need

391
00:21:47,840 --> 00:21:48,880
to dwell on this.

392
00:21:51,600 --> 00:21:52,760
My family has fallen into decline,

393
00:21:53,520 --> 00:21:54,840
but fortunately, master (Lord Shen) took me in.

394
00:21:55,760 --> 00:21:57,520
He has shown immense kindness to us Mos,

395
00:21:57,960 --> 00:21:59,720
treating me like his own son.

396
00:22:01,240 --> 00:22:02,320
Pleading before the late emperor

397
00:22:02,600 --> 00:22:04,080
is my responsibility.

398
00:22:04,480 --> 00:22:05,680
If I were to neglect this,

399
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:08,200
that would be disloyal and unjust.

400
00:22:08,880 --> 00:22:10,720
You sacrificed a promising future,

401
00:22:11,600 --> 00:22:13,680
exiled here with no hope for promotion,

402
00:22:14,360 --> 00:22:15,360
just to save a disloyal, unjust,

403
00:22:15,360 --> 00:22:17,120
and unfilial person like me,

404
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:18,880
merely to survive.

405
00:22:19,640 --> 00:22:20,960
Using my father's reputation

406
00:22:22,200 --> 00:22:24,120
to barter for my own bright future.

407
00:22:26,000 --> 00:22:26,800
Qianzhi,

408
00:22:29,720 --> 00:22:31,120
if you had known it would come to this,

409
00:22:34,640 --> 00:22:36,080
would you have regretted it?

410
00:22:38,880 --> 00:22:39,960
Looking back,

411
00:22:41,120 --> 00:22:42,880
I have many regrets,

412
00:22:44,000 --> 00:22:45,200
but saving you

413
00:22:47,200 --> 00:22:48,000
has never been one!

414
00:22:52,240 --> 00:22:53,480
What you did that day

415
00:22:54,280 --> 00:22:55,600
was an act of desperation.

416
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:57,280
Master in heaven

417
00:22:57,280 --> 00:22:58,360
will surely understand.

418
00:22:59,720 --> 00:23:00,800
"Your mother

419
00:23:01,360 --> 00:23:03,160
angrily driving you out of the house"

420
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:04,760
was merely a show

421
00:23:04,760 --> 00:23:05,840
to deceive those petty ones.

422
00:23:05,840 --> 00:23:07,120
It was just a distraction.

423
00:23:08,720 --> 00:23:09,520
What she truly wanted

424
00:23:10,000 --> 00:23:11,960
was to protect her only son.

425
00:23:12,520 --> 00:23:13,320
Qianzhi,

426
00:23:14,160 --> 00:23:15,440
do you really not blame me?

427
00:23:22,720 --> 00:23:23,920
Do you recognize this flower?

428
00:23:26,560 --> 00:23:27,360
I do.

429
00:23:29,760 --> 00:23:31,680
It's Xiuxiu's favorite flower, Tongzimian.

430
00:23:45,040 --> 00:23:45,840
[Where are we going?]

431
00:23:47,240 --> 00:23:48,320
[Hurry up!]

432
00:23:49,440 --> 00:23:50,160
[Look,]

433
00:23:50,160 --> 00:23:51,640
[Du has some real skills.]

434
00:23:51,840 --> 00:23:53,680
[He helped me raised Tongzimian.]

435
00:23:58,760 --> 00:23:59,560
[Du,]

436
00:24:00,040 --> 00:24:00,840
[you're about to]

437
00:24:00,920 --> 00:24:02,320
[spoil Mo Xiuxiu completely.]

438
00:24:03,320 --> 00:24:04,280
[Tongzimian is rare to grow,]

439
00:24:04,680 --> 00:24:06,000
[with dozens of peonies]

440
00:24:06,000 --> 00:24:07,360
[not necessarily yielding one.]

441
00:24:07,400 --> 00:24:08,480
[Other young ladies]

442
00:24:08,600 --> 00:24:09,400
[would be satisfied]

443
00:24:09,400 --> 00:24:10,400
[with just one peony on their head,]

444
00:24:10,400 --> 00:24:11,160
[but you]

445
00:24:11,240 --> 00:24:12,600
[insist on a Tongzimian.]

446
00:24:12,600 --> 00:24:13,400
[What's wrong with that?]

447
00:24:13,480 --> 00:24:14,800
[I just love it.]

448
00:24:15,240 --> 00:24:16,080
[Du,]

449
00:24:16,560 --> 00:24:17,480
[the one on my head]

450
00:24:17,480 --> 00:24:19,000
[will soon wither in a few days.]

451
00:24:19,240 --> 00:24:20,000
[When it comes to that,]

452
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:22,120
[remember to get the best one for me.]

453
00:24:22,120 --> 00:24:22,880
[Rest assured,]

454
00:24:22,920 --> 00:24:24,240
[I've already selected one.]

455
00:24:24,440 --> 00:24:26,040
[I'll pluck for you in a few days.]

456
00:24:29,600 --> 00:24:30,800
After Xiuxiu passed away,

457
00:24:31,320 --> 00:24:32,200
I created this courtyard

458
00:24:32,200 --> 00:24:33,760
filled with peonies in her memory.

459
00:24:34,680 --> 00:24:35,560
Only then did I truly understand

460
00:24:36,680 --> 00:24:37,680
how challenging it was for you

461
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:38,640
to cultivate

462
00:24:38,880 --> 00:24:40,200
that Tongzimian.

463
00:24:44,120 --> 00:24:44,920
Du,

464
00:24:45,760 --> 00:24:47,040
how could I ever hold grudges against you?

465
00:24:47,920 --> 00:24:49,160
I can only feel gratitude

466
00:24:50,160 --> 00:24:51,960
that you managed to adapt

467
00:24:52,480 --> 00:24:53,720
and live well.

468
00:24:54,800 --> 00:24:55,760
So in this world,

469
00:24:56,800 --> 00:24:58,560
there could be one more person like me

470
00:24:58,960 --> 00:25:00,160
who cherishes Xiuxiu

471
00:25:00,880 --> 00:25:02,120
and keeps her memory alive.

472
00:25:02,680 --> 00:25:03,720
Life is indeed unpredictable.

473
00:25:05,600 --> 00:25:06,840
I never imagined that

474
00:25:08,120 --> 00:25:09,640
our farewell in the capital would turn out

475
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:14,360
to be my final goodbye to Xiuxiu.

476
00:25:16,040 --> 00:25:17,480
If Xiuxiu were still alive,

477
00:25:18,800 --> 00:25:19,520
she would be

478
00:25:19,520 --> 00:25:21,000
about the same age as Lady Du now.

479
00:25:29,240 --> 00:25:30,040
Qianzhi, there's something

480
00:25:33,440 --> 00:25:35,160
I've always hesitated to ask.

481
00:25:40,320 --> 00:25:41,800
How did she die?

482
00:25:48,200 --> 00:25:49,640
It was my failure to care for her.

483
00:25:50,480 --> 00:25:51,440
She fell ill due to the

484
00:25:52,120 --> 00:25:52,920
unfamiliar environment.

485
00:26:01,480 --> 00:26:02,280
[Xiuxiu?]

486
00:26:03,200 --> 00:26:04,480
[I remember now,]

487
00:26:05,800 --> 00:26:07,480
[the rattan pig and the letter]

488
00:26:07,480 --> 00:26:09,160
[were gifts from Mo Xiuxiu.]

489
00:26:09,920 --> 00:26:11,440
[That's why he has kept them for so long.]

490
00:26:20,800 --> 00:26:21,600
Mo Xiuxiu,

491
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:23,640
what are you writing?

492
00:26:26,960 --> 00:26:27,760
Sir,

493
00:26:27,840 --> 00:26:29,280
you frightened them.

494
00:26:29,800 --> 00:26:30,920
It's nothing, nothing.

495
00:26:31,600 --> 00:26:33,000
Everyone, please continue your practice.

496
00:26:37,320 --> 00:26:38,560
It seems these children

497
00:26:39,360 --> 00:26:40,480
haven't yet moved on

498
00:26:40,480 --> 00:26:42,000
from the trauma of being kidnapped.

499
00:26:44,400 --> 00:26:45,200
Du,

500
00:26:45,480 --> 00:26:47,040
go collect some bulrushes.

501
00:26:47,040 --> 00:26:47,680
Sure!

502
00:26:53,880 --> 00:26:54,680
Sir.

503
00:26:57,520 --> 00:26:58,320
My lord.

504
00:26:58,800 --> 00:26:59,800
Let's conclude

505
00:26:59,800 --> 00:27:00,880
today's lesson here.

506
00:27:01,440 --> 00:27:02,240
Understood.

507
00:27:02,640 --> 00:27:03,440
Children,

508
00:27:04,280 --> 00:27:05,160
in a moment,

509
00:27:05,360 --> 00:27:06,640
I will teach you how to

510
00:27:07,040 --> 00:27:09,080
weave small animals with the bulrushes.

511
00:27:09,360 --> 00:27:10,160
Does that sound good?

512
00:27:10,240 --> 00:27:11,040
Yes!

513
00:27:18,440 --> 00:27:19,240
Du,

514
00:27:19,400 --> 00:27:21,000
am I doing this correctly?

515
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:23,720
Du,

516
00:27:24,200 --> 00:27:25,840
