517
00:27:55,880 --> 00:27:57,080
You're so talented!

518
00:27:57,360 --> 00:27:58,800
I want to weave one for Du

519
00:27:58,800 --> 00:28:00,160
as a birthday gift.

520
00:28:00,800 --> 00:28:02,440
Can we trade?

521
00:28:03,200 --> 00:28:04,440
Of course, take it!

522
00:28:07,720 --> 00:28:08,520
Thank you!

523
00:28:08,840 --> 00:28:10,200
What's your name?

524
00:28:10,480 --> 00:28:12,920
You can just call me Xing.

525
00:28:19,120 --> 00:28:20,200
[Because that was a gift]

526
00:28:20,200 --> 00:28:21,480
[from Mo Xiuxiu,]

527
00:28:22,240 --> 00:28:23,840
[that's why he's treasured it for so long.]

528
00:28:25,000 --> 00:28:26,280
[It turns out the one he truly loves]

529
00:28:26,840 --> 00:28:27,840
[is Mo Xiuxiu.]

530
00:28:46,880 --> 00:28:47,760
Today,

531
00:28:47,760 --> 00:28:49,360
you asked to meet in private.

532
00:28:49,760 --> 00:28:51,080
What is it about?

533
00:28:51,080 --> 00:28:51,920
The Shen Family has suffered injustice,

534
00:28:52,920 --> 00:28:54,200
and you're well aware of the details.

535
00:28:54,480 --> 00:28:55,800
I was still quite young back then,

536
00:28:55,920 --> 00:28:57,440
and many things remain unclear to me.

537
00:28:57,720 --> 00:28:59,640
I hope you can share the details with me.

538
00:29:02,120 --> 00:29:02,920
Lord Shen,

539
00:29:04,040 --> 00:29:04,920
it's all in the past.

540
00:29:04,920 --> 00:29:06,040
After so many years,

541
00:29:06,160 --> 00:29:07,400
You have achieved great success,

542
00:29:07,400 --> 00:29:08,520
with a bright future ahead of you.

543
00:29:08,760 --> 00:29:10,560
Don't let the past weigh you down.

544
00:29:14,920 --> 00:29:16,240
What do you mean by that?

545
00:29:17,040 --> 00:29:18,760
The suffering of imprisonment is something

546
00:29:19,400 --> 00:29:20,960
that ordinary people cannot bear.

547
00:29:21,400 --> 00:29:22,200
Du,

548
00:29:23,000 --> 00:29:24,240
now that you're free,

549
00:29:24,880 --> 00:29:26,800
don't dwell on seeking revenge.

550
00:29:28,160 --> 00:29:29,480
Du does not seek revenge.

551
00:29:31,920 --> 00:29:33,240
But I'm a member of the Shen Family.

552
00:29:36,520 --> 00:29:38,080
We deserve the truth.

553
00:29:47,760 --> 00:29:48,600
You are now highly trusted

554
00:29:48,600 --> 00:29:50,160
by Her Highness.

555
00:29:50,240 --> 00:29:51,560
As long as you maintain your stability,

556
00:29:51,800 --> 00:29:53,160
your future is boundless.

557
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:55,320
Do you truly have the courage

558
00:29:55,520 --> 00:29:56,200
to give up everything

559
00:29:56,200 --> 00:29:57,680
you currently possess?

560
00:29:57,920 --> 00:29:59,360
If you want to thoroughly investigate it,

561
00:29:59,440 --> 00:30:00,200
you must be prepared to give up

562
00:30:00,200 --> 00:30:01,640
everything you have now.

563
00:30:01,640 --> 00:30:02,560
Do you believe

564
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:04,120
it's worth it?

565
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:08,720
Throughout history, those who can

566
00:30:09,080 --> 00:30:10,280
investigate and overturn old cases

567
00:30:10,280 --> 00:30:11,720
are often those without vulnerabilities.

568
00:30:12,000 --> 00:30:13,280
Now that you're married,

569
00:30:13,960 --> 00:30:15,640
can you truly disregard everything,

570
00:30:15,960 --> 00:30:16,760
burn your bridges,

571
00:30:16,760 --> 00:30:18,080
and act solely for your own sake?

572
00:30:22,920 --> 00:30:24,080
I still maintain my stance:

573
00:30:25,080 --> 00:30:25,880
let's not revisit

574
00:30:27,080 --> 00:30:28,400
the past any further.

575
00:30:29,200 --> 00:30:30,000
Lord Shen,

576
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:31,360
the answer you seek

577
00:30:31,600 --> 00:30:33,000
has already been provided to you.

578
